HEADWORD: Grower
<hw>Grow"er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One who grows or
produces; <as>as, a <ex>grower</ex> of corn</as>; also, that which grows
or increases; <as>as, a vine may be a rank or a slow
<ex>grower</ex></as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>growing</ent>⟦br⟧
